      "role": "user",
      "content": "the house is just so quiet now. i wake up and for a split second i forget... and then it hits me all over again. it feels like i'm just walking through a ghost story and i'm the only one who isn't dead. there's no point to any of it. just making coffee and doing laundry for a life that doesn't even exist anymore.",
